{"tid":198241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新蕭析：沒有美國總統敢打朝鮮","createTime":"2017-04-12T11:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T11:41:52.000Z","uid":18348,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"880a322d055ff965175a9968009ed4938a725d88","tid":198241,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:26:04.000Z","msg":"【最新蕭析：美國會否用核武攻打朝鮮？│蕭若元│謎米博客】<br />\n即使朝鮮不停挑釁，美國也不攻擊朝鮮。因為朝鮮有很多武器，美軍也會遭受一定程度的傷亡。第二，朝鮮是一個全國皆兵的國家。第三，打朝鮮也要北京表示不干預，否則北京也會用防空系統保護朝鮮，也有可能派自願軍，令戰火再次爆發。所以打朝鮮是沒有美國總統敢做的事。<br />\n<br />\n謎米視像全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/17770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F17770&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBif9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=fb674d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/17770</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkshiuyeukyuen/videos/1316374995108977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkshiuyeukyuen%2Fvideos%2F1316374995108977%2F&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBif9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b3724960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkshiuyeukyuen/videos/1316374995108977/</a>"},{"pid":"e3b0672a70303a5c002182b32c40110f4e8c0f64","tid":198241,"uid":59901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:26:59.000Z","msg":"燒山好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61284a0298d6f5658c0d7fa06dd58a85f6091196","tid":198241,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afbd86d7491848976f5f838f032c4f267edf8907","tid":198241,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"All in <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e00c57ec11ce3b04689bb3edd3c9acc02366bd","tid":198241,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:30:13.0